ActParliament of Canada Act
SubjectTravel - Red Tape Reduction Commission ** Honourable Rob Moore **
PrecisOrder AUTHORIZING TRAVEL within Canada by the Honourable Rob Moore, Member of Parliament for the constituency of Fundy Royal, in his capacity as a member of the RED TAPE REDUCTION COMMISSION, during the term of the Commission, subject to air travel conditions equivalent to those set out under National Joint Council or Treasury Board policies with any exceptions as may be approved by the Treasury Board.
